# --- Diagram render cache ---
# Holds the downloaded Mermaid library (~3 MB) and throwaway build HTML;
# regenerated on demand by tools/render_diagrams.py. The rendered outputs
# (diagrams/*.svg, diagrams/*.png) are kept.
diagrams/_build/

