# --- Build artifacts (kept by default) ---
# datadict.sql is text and diffable, so it stays under version control.
# datadict.db is a binary SQLite file regenerable from the seeds with
# `python3 build_dict.py`. Uncomment the next line to track only the .sql dump.
# datadict.db
